 -- fehlix <fehlix@mxlinux.org>  Wed, 29 Apr 2026 06:48:45 -0400

chroot-rescue (0.2.6+4) mx; urgency=medium

  * Add btrfs subvolume detection with or without luks encryption.
  * Expand detection for “/@” root subvolumes, as used by Ubuntu, Debian,
  antiX, MX Linux, Arch and its derivatives, openSUSE, and Fedora/RHEL,
  by custom patterns (@rootfs, root, rootfs, ROOT) as well as the top level.
  * Warn when LUKS mapper name does not match crypttab, to prevent from becoming
  unbootable after installing kernel, DKMS package, or updating initramfs.

 -- fehlix <fehlix@mxlinux.org>  Fri, 24 Apr 2026 18:58:29 -0400

